            <title>[SPARK-42967] Fix SparkListenerTaskStart.stageAttemptId when a task is started after the stage is cancelled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-42967</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a task is started after the stage is cancelled, the stageAttemptId field in  SparkListenerTaskStart event is set to -1. This could lead to unexpected problem for subscribers of SparkListener because -1 is not a legal stageAttemptId.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
